Dedication to the game :

Switching between classes and coding sessions, or trying out other applications, isn't always easy.

For this example,
I'm offering a linear TI-89 script that will reset the configuration settings.

This is a configuration, complete as possible to the factory settings, but safer than manually via the Memory Menu.

You can easily change every settîngs to your own.

I hope you'll find useful to insert `customkil()` somewhere between your own settings.
